To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private RickshawMan _rickshawman;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_rickshawman = RickshawMan(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_rickshawman.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "rickshawman", _rickshawman.Current.Value);
}
